{"tid":386862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"17歲逆子嫌買錯飲品　拐杖打到父母逃落樓","createTime":"2017-09-04T08:16:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-04T12:26:42.000Z","uid":11050,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a046a1574d8b0296ea8866ba4e2dda96bdaf15b3","tid":386862,"uid":11050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:16:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170904%2Fbkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html&d=yi%2F7EqKC%2F1bKY62EeZaE8jA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=095ee57e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170904/bkn-20170904015252662-0904_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n沙田發生逆子毆打父母事件。消息指，昨晚11時許，博泉街水泉澳邨嶺泉樓一名83歲姓楊老翁，替其17歲兒子買飯，回到家卻被嫌棄飲品冷熱出錯，兒子與其老父及姓黃(54歲)的母親發生激烈爭吵。期間，逆子情緒激動，不但喝罵父母，更出手以老父的枴杖毆打兩老，兩老分別頭及手受傷，負傷逃出屋外，並到樓下大堂向當值保安求助，由保安代為報案。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報到場，以涉嫌襲擊致造成身體實際傷害將少年拘捕，案件交由沙田警區刑事調查隊跟進。兩名傷者由救護車送院治理。"},{"pid":"f030b5ffd477d374988dfffbce842caffc75ce9d","tid":386862,"uid":76314,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:19:56.000Z","msg":"83歲老父同54歲老母，重唔係廢老娶大陸閪咩，之後生個蝗子就唔撚識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b42ffb557bfacd45fe275d26a5decebe1ff336d0","tid":386862,"uid":26816,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:22:31.000Z","msg":"66歲仲老當益壯生左舊忤逆仔出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做得佢呀爺啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6de238cb931a87b4ac9c8d98fa2acb239cf40c84","tid":386862,"uid":60074,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:22:42.000Z","msg":"重以為psp<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7608d6be470e06ef974c9d3ed6c7eeabdc4226e5","tid":386862,"uid":65756,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:23:19.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係法式麵包"},{"pid":"b26fdb8cf0280397783bfa1504840df76b17457a","tid":386862,"uid":28279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:31:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>83歲老父同54歲老母，重唔係廢老娶大陸閪咩，之後生個蝗子就唔撚識教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肯撚定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4932002ce9742ff19b3eed983135f60e29a0fb15","tid":386862,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"唔係psp？"},{"pid":"d23c17f8a458d3370257c6eeb33e30f6888bbefa","tid":386862,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:33:13.000Z","msg":"83歲姓楊老翁，替其17歲兒子買飯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98b9cc50bd15014a0b3e19e3e568aa076825546","tid":386862,"uid":32028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:34:24.000Z","msg":"根據調查，少年和父親（42歲）約好，要父親替他購買於12月12日發售的攜帶遊戲機PSP。不過從早上就去排隊的父親，卻買回了別的遊戲機，這讓少年相當惱火。在吃早飯時，少年拿起放在餐桌上的水果刀旁邊的法式麵包（長30厘米），不斷毆打父親。<br />\n<br />\n聽到父親的慘叫的母親急忙來阻止了少年，不過父親的額頭還是受了輕微的毆傷。少年被附近接到報告的警察逮捕。在調查中少年供訴到：「一想到他那麼早出去到底去排了什麼隊，就惱火的不得了。」<br />\n<br />\n警視廳表示，今後類似這種由於親子間對遊戲的理解溝通不充分，而引發的暴力事件，還將有可能發生，請大家引以為戒。"},{"pid":"6ed4afcdc87118b4dba9a1490bd3a10e12a447ad","tid":386862,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50f02d8764cd7a427118fd34e81497dcfa10d8e1","tid":386862,"uid":32006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:38:44.000Z","msg":"逃走到咁有勇有謀<br />\n+1分啦得掛校長?"},{"pid":"afa0755f808a49f4ad30be3b15ea45e22a76b14a","tid":386862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T08:44:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>37歲生個仔出黎</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">83歲姓楊老翁，替其17歲兒子</span>"},{"pid":"f115de10633fd09c6685cbdc818b1661162dbd7f","tid":386862,"uid":1